OL,3,CMother welcomes plans for mandatory
OL,4,Ceye tests for over 70s after son's
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,FThe tests are part of a new government
OL,8,Fproposals to make roads safer,
OL,9,Fincluding reducing the drink drive
OL,10,Flimit - and a minimum learning period
OL,11,Ffor new drivers.
OL,13,FNeil Colquhoun, 28, from Hook was on
OL,14,Fhis way home from work in Basingstoke
OL,15,Fat 6:45pm on 11 March 2011, when the
OL,16,Fcollision happened on the A30.
OL,18,FHe was hit by a car travelling the
OL,19,Fwrong way down the dual carriageway.
OL,20,FBefore members of the public could
OL,21,Frescue Neil, the car caught fire.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/9
