OL,7,FNeil died at the scene.
OL,9,FSpeaking to ITV Meridian Patricia
OL,10,Fwho's known as Pat said: "It doesn't
OL,11,Fget any easier, even though it's
OL,12,Fnearly 15 years now.
OL,14,F"The gentleman who caused this
OL,15,Faccident, he was 89 years old, he was
OL,16,Fblind in one eye, and he was driving
OL,17,Fat night, and it should never have
OL,18,Fhappened.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/9
