OL,3,CMother welcomes plans for mandatory
OL,4,Ceye tests for over 70s after son's
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,F"Why didn't his family stop him from
OL,8,Fdriving? They didn't do anything, they
OL,9,Fjust let him carry on."
OL,11,FPatricia is welcoming a Government
OL,12,Fannouncement on Wednesday (7 January)
OL,13,Ffor a consultation on mandatory
OL,14,Feyesight testing for those over 70.
OL,16,FThe Government said the plans would
OL,17,Fsave lives and build a safer future
OL,18,Ffor all UK road users, and options for
OL,19,Fcognitive testing will also be
OL,20,Fdeveloped to protect road users.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/9
