OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,FLocal Transport Minister Lilian
OL,8,FGreenwood MP said: "We know that 90%
OL,9,Fof road traffic collisions are
OL,10,Fpreventable.
OL,12,F"We think that that number of deaths
OL,13,Fand serious injuries is unacceptable
OL,14,Fon our roads and we need to take
OL,15,Faction.
OL,17,F"In fact we have a duty to take action
OL,18,Fto reduce it."
