OL,3,CMother welcomes plans for mandatory
OL,4,Ceye tests for over 70s after son's
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,FChief Executive at Association of
OL,8,FOptometrists, Adam Sampson said:
OL,9,F"We're very pleased with what the
OL,10,Fgovernment has announced.
OL,12,F"We've been, as an organisation,
OL,13,Fcampaigning for many years to get
OL,14,Fgovernment to take seriously the issue
OL,15,Fof drivers on the roads, particularly
OL,16,Felderly drivers, who are not capable
OL,17,Fof driving safely because their vision
OL,18,Fis not up to scratch.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
