OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,F"I was at an inquest last year with
OL,8,Fthree families who'd lost loved ones
OL,9,Fbecause of this sort of situation."
OL,11,FSpeaking about her son, Pat added:
OL,12,F"He's missed out on so much.
OL,14,F"He could be married by now, he could
OL,15,Fhave had a family, he's missed all
OL,16,Fthat, but I miss him every day.
OL,18,F"His brother's miss him, his father
OL,19,Fmisses him.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/9
